title: The Creator - Flawed Brilliance
description: The Creator, written and directed by Gareth Edwards, is a highly ambitious new science fiction movie that manages to do a lot on its $80 Million budget, but suffers from a slightly muddled script that isn't quite able to juggle its many themes and characters.
